  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* feat(xml): Preserve comments and processing instructions (#175) by @takeokunn in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/508\r\n* Bump github.com/charmbracelet/bubbles from 0.21.1 to 1.0.0 by @dependabot[bot] in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/515\r\n* Correctly handle spread operator within array construction by @TomWright in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/520\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @takeokunn made their first contribution in https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/pull/508\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/TomWright/dasel/compare/v3.2.2...v3.2.3",
